  "description": [
    "l s A i crhe OHIO Daytonians Get Appointment At NAACP Conference The executive committee of the Ohio civil rights NAACP confer ence was completed Tuesday with the announcement that Miley O Williamson of Dayton has been appointed to that body There are nine other members of the com mittee The organization is com posed of Negro and interracial or ganizations in the state Other Dayton affiliates of the conference include Rev H Laur ence McNeil pastof the Zion Bap tist church and George Weaver director of the National committee to Abolish Discrimination of the CIO The Ohio civil rights conference was organized to supplement the work in the field of civil rights Iseing done by other organizations It is not the same group men tioned in these pages earlier this week That group was the Day ton civil rights committee It is PreFight Predictions Go Wanting in Louis Walcott Bout By Jimmie N Ji Your reporter having used up much effort and energy in trying to bring out the predictions of taytons fight fans regarding the championship fight between Joe Louis and Jersey Joe Walcott find it a hard job More than 90 per cent of the experts show"
